{"tid":2064050,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"同樣係整嘢食，中菜師傅同壽司師傅完全係不同層次","createTime":"2020-06-14T13:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T09:25:33.000Z","uid":130722,"like":3,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a738b9541f673b4ed505810d632345cfa6101a02","tid":2064050,"uid":130722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:44:48.000Z","msg":"煮米/握功/刀功/舍利/酢漬/熟成/溫度/酒肴樣樣都要學，淨係識一樣冇可能做師傅，包羅萬有，難學難精。<br />\n<br />\n中菜「師傅」就咁比啲味水，夠猛火獲氣，唔係話冇技術，但呢啲嘢求其搵個阿嬸練幾年都精通到，唔係吹奏自己但我煮開公仔麵都整到中菜<br />\n<br />\n中菜好食係睇舊食材本身靚唔靚，師傅最多關掌廚果個有冇心機炒好比你事，發自內心唔覺得有咩資格開到成行成市<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n窮撚食過垃圾壽司就收皮啦"},{"pid":"b13190deadbf12924c65f85d433cfbd6ae4e64a6","tid":2064050,"uid":33359,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:46:32.000Z","msg":"有邊個菜系D野好食唔係睇舊食材靚唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edabb0571341509213471f3616315910e8ea4c01","tid":2064050,"uid":27915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:46:41.000Z","msg":"連/高登神枱級嘅中菜今日終於收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec79bcbacfca3587f3e7b2494aa51c9f7bfd781","tid":2064050,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T13:48:20.000Z","msg":"想點呀又出<br />\n同樣係整嘢食，壽司師傅同中廚師傅完全係不同層次<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2063893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2063893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f82e460163f